<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.7.5">
<l>viṭṭilaṅku ceñcōtit tāmaraip pātaṅ kaikaḷkaṇkaḷ</l>
<l>viṭṭilaṅku karuñcuṭar malaiyē tiruvuṭampu</l>
<l>viṭṭilaṅku matiyañ cīrcaṅku cakkaram pariti</l>
<l>viṭṭilaṅku muṭiyammāṉ matucū taṉaṉṟa ṉakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bright-shining red radiant lotuses are the feet, hand [and] eyes,</l>
<l>a bright-shining dark glowing mountain the sacred body,</l>
<l>of the excellence of the bright-shining moon the conch [and] discus,</l>
<l>bright-shinig [like] the sun the crown of him, the lord, Madhusūdana.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
